                    subpoenaed or asked to testify before
                    any legislative body concerning fraud
                    or abuse with regard to the purchase
                    or sale of goods or services?
                </label>

                <div class="form-check">
                    <input asp-for="F8"
                           class="form-check-input"
                           type="radio"
                           id="F8a"
                           value="Yes">
                    <label class="form-check-label"
                           for="F8a">
