                       style="font-weight: 500;">
                    9. Has the COMPANY, any COMPANY Leader
                    or COMPANY Employee ever been found guilty
                    of any violations of laws governing the
                    regulation of antitrust practices or
                    been deposed or subpoenaed in connection
                    with any litigation or investigation
                    involving such laws?
                </label>

                <div class="form-check">
                    <input asp-for="F9"
                           class="form-check-input"
                           type="radio"
                           id="F9a"
                           value="Yes">
                    <label class="form-check-label"
