            </div>

            <div class="mt-2">
                <label class="text-justify mb-0"
                       style="font-weight: 500;">
                    10. Has the COMPANY, any COMPANY Leader
                    or COMPANY Employee ever been mentioned
                    by name in the press (i.e. article in
                    newspaper, magazine or online vehicles)
                    as having violated anti-corruption or
                    anti-trust laws?
                </label>

                <div class="form-check">
                    <input asp-for="F10"
