                       style="font-weight: 500;">
                    13. Is the COMPANY, any COMPANY
                    Leader or COMPANY Employee
                    currently named on any of the
                    following lists?
                </label>
                <br />
                <label class="text-justify mb-0"
                       style="font-weight: 400;">
                    a. The Specially Designated Nationals List (the “SDN”)
                </label>

                <div class="form-check">
                    <input asp-for="F13A"
                           class="form-check-input"
                           type="radio"
                           id="F13Aa"
                           value="Yes">
                    <label class="form-check-label"
